/>\n兩邊都唔啱，屌架車啦</blockquote><br />\n行人有咩唔岩？"},{"pid":"2a43c41f96eadd1e439ab4866b2dd3fd1d3deab5","tid":232631,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:26:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>司機衝燈<br />\n連登仔竟然屌行人唔屌司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩邊都唔啱，屌架車啦</blockquote><br />\n行人有咩唔岩？</blockquote><br />\n行人都唔啱 on99"},{"pid":"d34c4095924b74af912d933ab9df467d5c9fa179","tid":232631,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:29:47.000Z","msg":"紅燈連人都睇唔到"},{"pid":"fad25a5d407545c08ca10e076a513bd658c3c958","tid":232631,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:30:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>司機衝燈<br />\n連登仔竟然屌行人唔屌司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為雙程證呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7c9e366d39d978346eadd729181a656e5f8fedd","tid":232631,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:32:18.000Z","msg":"個司機係咪女人黎"},{"pid":"b6e6928ecd8957cd63d1b5cd1efae31bd87dd27d","tid":232631,"uid":33004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>司機衝燈<br />\n連登仔竟然屌行人唔屌司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩邊都唔啱，屌架車啦</blockquote><br />\n行人有咩唔岩？</blockquote><br />\n行人都唔啱 on99</blockquote><br />\n大陸哩就一定唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對人唔對事"},{"pid":"fcb5b7d18ff290218bd06e0ca36c83cd4a1264a2","tid":232631,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"cls"},{"pid":"0caa33e1868e08f80822bc3f330a5e4d417dab1b","tid":232631,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T04:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>司機衝燈<br 